Members of the Gauteng executive committee will
undergo lifestyle audits.This is according to the MPL Jack Bloom in a
statement.Bloom said this information was disclosed by the
Gauteng Finance MEC Barbara Creecy, who was replying to his questions in the
Gauteng Legislature on behalf of Premier David Makhura in his absence on
